      "description": "This E92 M3 represents a superb mechanical specimen featuring the legendary S65 4.0L V8 and a tactile 6-speed manual transmission. The high-revving, naturally aspirated powerplant delivers linear torque through the M-Variable differential, while the chassis remains composed thanks to Electronic Damper Control (EDC) with calibrated damping rates. Preventative maintenance is up to date, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the valvetrain and VANOS system perform at peak efficiency. Riding on staggered Style 359M alloys wrapped in Michelin Pilot Sport 4S tires, this unit offers the precise turn-in and longitudinal grip expected of a well-sorted M-division product.",
