      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2019 Lexus RX 350 in Atomic Silver. This vehicle strikes a perfect balance between luxury and daily utility. The exterior paint retains a brilliant luster, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood consistent with highway driving. The interior is a standout feature, finished in pristine Parchment leather that has been treated regularly to prevent wear; it remains supple and free of any cracks or stains. All onboard technology, including the navigation system, heated/ventilated seats, and the premium surround-sound system, functions exactly as it did the day it left the showroom. Mechanically, this Lexus is sound, featuring a smooth-shifting 8-speed transmission and a quiet, responsive V6 engine. I have kept a detailed log of all scheduled maintenance performed at the local dealership, including the most recent 60,000-mile service which included a full fluid flush and brake inspection. The tires are high-quality Michelins with approximately 70% tread remaining. This is a non-smoker vehicle with a clean title, ready for a new home.",
